          "value": "turn=start, \ndamageRoll=1d4, damageType=necrotic,\nlabel=Bleeding,\ndamageBeforeSave=true,\nactionSave=dialog,\nsaveRemove=true,\nsaveDC=15,\nchatFlavor=Lil paper cut fr,\nrollType=skill,\nsaveAbility=med,\nfastForwardDamage=true,",
